        "rich_text_Lgzp8A": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Diamonds have always been tied to the ideas of eternity and commitment. Lately, they’ve gotten a whole lot more colorful. Be it pinks, blues, yellows, it’s not just a trend, it’s a shift.</p><p>For a long time, colored diamonds were something most people only saw in museums or on a celebrity’s finger but thanks to Lab Grown Diamonds, these dreamy shades are finally within reach for everyone to cherish. These gems are as meaningful as they are beautiful.</p><p>Let’s take a closer look at why colored Lab Grown Diamonds are gaining popularity and why they might just be the perfect fit for you, too.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xMGDpJ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What Are Colored Lab Grown Diamonds?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>What Are Colored Lab Grown Diamonds?</h2>",
            "custom_id": "what",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_zckrpQ": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/What_Are_Colored_Lab_Grown_Diamonds.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_QtqiEz": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Colored Lab Grown Diamonds are synthetic diamonds created in a laboratory that exhibit vibrant hues such as pink, blue, yellow, green, and more. These diamonds share the same chemical composition, crystal structure, and physical properties as natural diamonds, but they are grown under controlled conditions that allow for the introduction of specific colors. </p><p>Scientists use methods like HPHT (High Pressure, High Temperature) or CVD (Chemical Vapor Deposition) to mimic how diamonds naturally form, just with a lot more control.</p><p>Different elements added during the growth process (like nitrogen or boron) or special treatments afterward can give these diamonds their color. </p><ul><li>Yellow: Caused by nitrogen impurities.</li><li>Blue: Typically due to the presence of boron.</li><li>Pink and Red: Achieved through plastic deformation (structural changes during formation or treatment).</li><li>Green: Often the result of exposure to radiation during or after growth.</li><li>Purple, Orange, Black: Can be engineered through various treatments or element combinations.</li></ul>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_eUYCXy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Here’s Why Everyone’s Talking About Them",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Here’s Why Everyone’s Talking About Them</h2><p>So what’s fueling the rise of these colorful stones? Let’s find out!</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_A39FM4": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1. They Feel Personal",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>1. They Feel Personal</h3>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_3TkqtV": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/They_Feel_Personal_1080_300.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Today’s couples don’t always want to stick to tradition. They want <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-rings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">rings</span></a> that say something about their story, about who they are and what they love. A soft pink for the romantic, a deep blue for the calm and steady one, a golden yellow for someone who lights up a room, every Colored Lab Grown Diamond tells a story.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "blue-gemstone-with-oval-diamond-ring",
