            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_gbBNyF": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "4. They’re All Over the Red Carpet",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>4. They’re All Over the Red Carpet</h3><p>Whether it was J.Lo’s Pink Diamond years ago or more recent colored stunners on social media, it’s clear these stones are having a moment.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_HwqhEM": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Meet the Colors",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Meet the Colors</h2><p>Each shade comes with its own kind of magic. Pick the one that speaks directly to your soul.</p><p>Pink Diamonds<br/>Soft, romantic, and full of charm. These are perfect if you want something feminine with a twist. Whether it’s a light blush or something bolder like rose, pink diamonds feel warm and full of love.</p><p>Blue Diamonds<br/>Cool, calming, and just a little mysterious. The tones can go from icy blue to rich sapphire-like shades. They’re ideal for someone who wants something elegant and quietly powerful.</p><p>Yellow Diamonds<br/>Bright and bold, yellow stones bring sunshine to your hand. They stand out in a crowd and are perfect for someone who’s not afraid to make a statement.</p><p>Greens, Champagnes, and Beyond<br/>The range is growing fast. Think earthy greens, soft golden champagnes, even diamonds with two tones that shift in the light. If you want a ring that feels different, this is where it gets really exciting.</p>",
            "custom_id": "colors",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6qzxWD": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Will It Last?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Will It Last?</h2><p>Lab Grown Colored Diamonds are just as hard and durable as Natural Diamonds, ranking a 10 on the Mohs scale. That means they’re built for everyday wear, just like any traditional diamond. The color doesn’t wear off or fade. It’s part of the stone itself.</p><p>At Lucira, every stone goes through detailed checks to make sure the color, cut, carat and clarity all live up to the standard, because this isn’t just jewelry, it is a story.</p>",
            "custom_id": "last",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_CEGKJP": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Choosing the Right Setting",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Choosing the Right Setting</h2><p>How you set the diamond can totally change the vibe. Here are a few quick tips:</p>",
            "custom_id": "setting",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
