        "rich_text_ak9VMA": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Should You Go for One?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Should You Go for One?</h2><p>For those who want something a little different, something with personality, heart, and meaning, a colored lab grown diamond might be exactly what you're looking for.</p><p>They’re not just beautiful. They’re expressive and unique. And they let you choose a ring that’s as unique as your love.</p><p>So when you're ready to pick the one that tells your story, <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira Jewelry</a> is here to help.</p>",
